. Hi @salayev ,

Validation vs required is a surprisingly difficult concept. `validations` is related to `showError()` and `getErrorMessages()`. `required` is related to `showRequired()`. So you never check errors related to required. The reason is that they are two different things. You want to indicate a required input differently than when a validation is wrong :-)
- validations prop => showError() / getErrorMessages()
- required prop => showRequired()
